HEADWORD: Unstriped
<hw>Un*striped"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
striped.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Nat. Hist.)</fld> <def>Without marks or striations;
nonstriated; <as>as, <ex>unstriped</ex> muscle fibers</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unstudied</ent>⟦br⟧
